                  "status": "Open",
                  "severity": "Medium",
                  "type": "Disclosure of information",
                  "description": "A direct consequence of compromised accounts is the unauthorized disclosure of personal information. An attacker with access to a user's account on Alovoa could potentially access or expose private conversations, personal preferences, photos, and other sensitive data designed to be shared only with chosen individuals on the platform.",
                  "mitigation": "Provide remediation for this threat or a reason if status is N/A",
